# 14x6 wall-mounted meeting screen (TV / projector display) — hangs on
# the back wall above the seating area. Bezel = M (dark frame), screen
# face = j (powered-on dark wallpaper) with a c (cyan) accent strip to
# read as "screen is on, showing slide deck."
@frame 0
M M M M M M M M M M M M M M
M j j j j j j j j j j j j M
M j c c c c c c c c c c j M
M j j j j j j j j j j j j M
M M M M M M M M M M M M M M
. . n n . . . . . . n n . .
